Configuration Zigbee pour ESP32-H2 (ESP-IDF 5.3.1)
Note: Zigbee requires esp-zigbee-lib external component (not in ESP-IDF 5.3.1 base)
Use menuconfig to enable necessary options if needed

These configs may not be available in standard IDF 5.3.1
# CONFIG_ZB_ENABLED=y
# CONFIG_ZB_ZCZR=y
# CONFIG_ZB_ZED=y

# Configuration LED Strip
CONFIG_LED_STRIP_ENABLED=y

# Power Management (optionnel, pour Light Sleep)
# CONFIG_PM_ENABLE=y
# CONFIG_FREERTOS_USE_TICKLESS_IDLE=y
